title: Big Ben to be switched of for four months as 'urgent' £40 million clock repairs ...
text: Big Ben is set to be switched off for four months - the longest period in its 156-year history - to allow urgent £40 million repairs to take place, MPs have been urged to take immediate action to save the iconic clock tower above the Houses
